sorry daddy is a 2015 bollywood action drama film directed by vijay pal .   starring shameem khan and tinu verma in the lead roles , it was produced by wasim khan under the s k films films banners .   set in the early 2014s , sorry daddy is a children story centring on the turbulent relationship between inspector shameem and children , a relationship which is affected by children 's issues with alcohol abuse and temperament .   the film released on 11 september 2015 .